‘S e dùthaich eileanach ann an [[Àisia]] a tha ann an 
'''Bachrain'''<ref>[http://www.akerbeltz.org/faclair/toraidhean.php?search=Bahrain&gaidhlignobeurla=beurla     Faclair Akerbeltz]</ref> neo 
'''Bairean'''<ref>Feuch Facal, Gairm (1995), ISBN 1871901391</ref> neo '''Bairèin'''<ref>[http://www.smo.uhi.ac.uk/gaidhlig/faclair/cuspair/duthchannan/  Dùthchannan ag SMO]</ref> neo 
'''Bahrain'''<ref>Map-balla an t-Saoghail,  Stòrlann Nàiseanta (2003),  ISBN 0007692714</ref>, ainm oifigeil  '''Rioghach Bhachrain''' 
([[Arabais]]|'''<big> مملكة البحرين </big>''', ''Mamlakat al-Barayn''). Tha i suidhichte anns a’ [[An Camas Mòr|Chamas Mhòr]].

Tha [[Saud-Aràibia]] san iar dhith, tha iad ceangailte leis an drochaid ris an canar ''King Fahd Causeway''. Dh’fhosgail an drochaid anns an  25mh an t-Samhain, [[1986]]. 
Tha planaichean aca drochaid eile a thogail eadar Bachrain agus [[Catar]], an ''Qatar–Bahrain Friendship Bridge''. Bhiodh sin an drochaid as fhaide air feadh an t-Saoghail. <ref>[http://www.cowi.com/cowi/en/menu/news/newsarchive/2001/danesbehindtheworldslongestfixedlink.htm Danes behind the world's longest fixed link]</ref>.

